{"tid":1491279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戰！","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T11:24:04.000Z","uid":289747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86c89b43733fd932d78009ccba379d05ee99de86","tid":1491279,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"從古至今，沒有一個極權管治是只用&ldquo;和理非&rdquo;嘅方法去推翻的。<br />\n<br />\n從古至今，&ldquo;勇武&rdquo;是推翻一個極權管治的手段，而&ldquo;和理非&rdquo;是這種手段的後盾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;和派&gt;及&lt;勇派&gt;，彼此依存，唇亡齒寒，缺一不可！<br />\n勇派為這場革命執行義務，和派為這個義務履行權力。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">千萬不要讓和理非的光環籠罩抗爭運動的道路</span>，否則只會步入雨傘運動的後塵！<br />\n嚟點我哋大家都十分清楚！！！對吧！<br />\n<br />\n818和理非流水式集會後，港共政權告訴香港人 : 當社會回復平靜後，真誠的對話就會展開。<br />\n<br />\nDKLM啦！bat zi soh wai !<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武從來都無退過場，亦唔會退場！<br />\n直到五大訴求可以一一落實為止！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足巴絲 : <br />\n你們還未清醒？<br />\n你們還未醒覺？<br />\n你們忘記雨傘運動是如何失敗的？<br />\n你們還擁抱818這個和理非的光環？(擁抱一下好啦)<br />\n你們還未察覺港共語言偽術的丑陋？<br />\n你們還未清楚共產黨的輿論手段？<br />\n你們忘記了有七百多位手足被捕？<br />\n你們忘記了有六名義士(事實上不止)的犧牲？<br />\n同時忘記了他們的遺言......!!!???<br />\n<br />\n醒吓啦！這是一場漫長嘅抗爭！漫長嘅革命！<br />\n必須要堅持到底！堅定不移！絕不畏懼！<br />\n<br />\n作為勇武一員，每次出去都走在最前線，因為我深信 : <br />\n在我背後嘅手足會支持住我，頂住我！所以我願意，我真的願意為這場抗爭履行義務！<br />\n<br />\n但係！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;請你們知道，勇武可以為和理非擋子彈，可以為你們負刑責，可以為你們流血傷亡！請你們也不要畏縮，亦不要見好就收，更不要輕易相信港共狗官的謊言，且有任何主動擁抱和理非嘅念頭！&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">擁抱和理非嘅光環，只會注定失敗！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為要光復香港，就必須要時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為沒有真雙普選，其他四大訴求就如condom！</span></span></span>所以五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<br />\n因為若只用和理非的方法而可以成功的話，今天的抗爭就不會出現！<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲手足 : <br />\n我真的不要甚麼美好的抗爭回憶，<br />\n我更加不要任何感動的抗爭片段，<br />\n我只要結果！我只要結果！我只要結果！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n真雙普選，港人治港！<br />\n不達目的，一齊攬炒！<br />\n寧化飛灰，不作浮塵！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3dba88c9a1c1d0b5f0de1e712b8d85a619d60803","tid":1491279,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:08:25.000Z","msg":"勇武絕不能退場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445e3bd8c47fa151543493a62059983a7f174d60","tid":1491279,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"勇武絕不能退場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf7121950bd548f56094ee357b2e01b35407935","tid":1491279,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:08:54.000Z","msg":"勇武絕不能退場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fd6ec80541ad01a21845e15ba2646a753e3858","tid":1491279,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"之後嘅文宣重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察=黑社會恐怖分子，撐警=支持恐怖主義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n外國支持恐怖主義拉得<br />\n<br />\n期待大規模，麻包袋對狗全家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申，斬首都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"b09a1bc072fff0476b1556c2627a0c99782ca6b1","tid":1491279,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:12:40.000Z","msg":"之後嘅文宣重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警察=黑社會恐怖分子，撐警=支持恐怖主義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n外國支持恐怖主義拉得<br />\n<br />\n期待大規模，麻包袋對狗全家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">利申，斬首都唔割</span></span>"},{"pid":"903a0aadc4db43e8d01f4a3611bd79a9dc9c901e","tid":1491279,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係時候開戰！"},{"pid":"fc232a00b05a801714fc28c00b5016228f7d24b5","tid":1491279,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:22:30.000Z","msg":"而家好多報導同輿論都大肆宣傳818和理非集會，<br />\n講到幾好幾和平，又乜又柒！<br />\n目的就係逼勇武退場！我DKLM！<br />\n我相信泛民都有人係咁諗！<br />\n<br />\n唇亡齒寒呀！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">單靠和理非如果成功的話，雨傘運動點解會失敗！</span><br />\n<br />\n如果和理非行動最後騎劫了整場抗爭運動的話，<br />\n我敢講 : 失敗離我們不遠了！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不分化 不割蓆 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&lt;勇&gt; &lt;和&gt; 缺一不可！</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa6ec16cd2049252833af7b824a1a289cd6cdfdd","tid":1491279,"uid":289747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}